#: data/levels/revenge_in_redmond/intro.stl:3
msgid "A Blast From The Past"
msgstr "Povratak u prošlost"

#: data/levels/revenge_in_redmond/intro.txt:4
msgid ""
"-A Blast From The Past!\n"
" Or was it a dream?\n"
"\n"
"\tTux and Gown were having a nice picnic,\n"
"\twhen suddenly, Gown is beamed away!!!\n"
"\t\n"
"\tWait a second... Gown?\n"
"\tWho is this penguin that looks\n"
"\tan awful lot like his friend Penny?\n"
"\t\n"
"\tAlso, a helicopter?\n"
"\tSince when do helicopters casually fly\n"
"\tover Antarctica and abduct penguins?\n"
"\t\n"
"\tEven though Tux was visibly confused\n"
"\tabout the events that just transpired,\n"
"\the could not just stand there\n"
"\tdoing nothing. Therefore, he\n"
"\tgave chase to rescue this\n"
"\tpoor penguin girl!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"*This looks like a job for ---\n"
"\t\n"
"-Super Tux"
msgstr ""
"-Povratak u prošlost!\n"
"Ili je to bio san?\n"
"\n"
"\tTux i Gown uživali su u pikniku,\n"
"\tkada je odjednom Gown teleportiran!!!\n"
"\t\n"
"\tČekaj malo... Gown?\n"
"\tTko je ovaj pingvin koji strašno\n"
"\tpodsjeća na njegovu prijateljicu Penny?\n"
"\t\n"
"\tI helikopter?\n"
"\tOtkad helikopteri bezbrižno lete iznad\n"
"\tAntarktike i otimaju pingvine?\n"
"\t\n"
"\tIako je Tux bio vidljivo zbunjen\n"
"\tdogađajima koji su se upravo odvili,\n"
"\tnije mogao samo stajati i ne poduzeti ništa.\n"
"\tStoga je krenuo u potjeru kako bi spasio\n"
"\tovu jadnu pingvinku!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"*Ovo izgleda kao posao za ---\n"
"\n"
"-Super Tux-a"

#: data/levels/revenge_in_redmond/long_office_nights.stl:3
msgid "Long Office Nights"
msgstr "Duge uredske noći"

#: data/levels/revenge_in_redmond/outro.stl:3
msgid "Where Is Everyone?"
msgstr "Gdje su svi?"

#: data/levels/revenge_in_redmond/outro.txt:4
msgid ""
"-Where Is Everyone?\n"
"\n"
"\tTux ran into the castle's throne room,\n"
"\tfrantically searching for the penguin girl Gown.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tAlas, he found neither Gown, nor the pilot\n"
"\tof the helicopter there, but instead, a statue.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tIt depicted a scaly creature with crossed arms.\n"
"\tThe pedestal it resided on was inscribed\n"
"\twith the word \"Nolok\". Was it a name?\n"
"\t\n"
"\tHe was unsure who or what\n"
"\tthis statue was depicting.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tAll of a sudden, Tux remembered...\n"
"\t\n"
"\tHe and Penny were ambushed\n"
"\tby this exact creature,\n"
"\tduring their picnic on the ice fields!\n"
"\t\n"
"\tTux opened his eyes. He was back\n"
"\tat the ice fields near the shore.\n"
"\tPenny, however, was gone.\n"
"\tShocked by this, he began looking around,\n"
"\tbut all he could find was a note...\n"
"\t\n"
"\t...from Nolok.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"-The End\n"
" Or rather, the beginning...?"
msgstr ""
"-Gdje su svi?\n"
"\n"
"\tTux je utrčao u dvoranu s prijestoljem dvorca,\n"
"\tpanično tražeći pingvinsku djevojku Gown.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tNažalost, ondje nije našao ni Gown ni\n"
"\tpilota helikoptera, već kip.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tPrikazivao je stvorenje prekriveno\n"
"ljuskama s prekriženim rukama.\n"
"\tNa postolju na kojem je stajala bio je\n"
"\turezan natpis \"Nolok\". Je li to bilo ime?\n"
"\\t\n"
"\tNije bio siguran koga ili što\n"
"\tta statua prikazuje.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tOdjednom se Tux sjetio...\n"
"\t\n"
"\tOn i Penny su bili napadnuti iz zasjede\n"
"\tupravo od tog stvorenja tijekom njihovog\n"
"\tpiknika na ledenim poljima!\n"
"\t\n"
"\tTux je otvorio oči. Vratio se na ledenja\n"
"\tpolja blizu obale. Penny, međutim, nije bilo.\n"
"\tŠokiran time, počeo je gledati oko sebe, ali sve\n"
"\tšto je mogao pronaći bila je poruka…\n"
"\t\n"
"...od Noloka.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"-Kraj\n"
" Ili, bolje rečeno, početak...?"

